query: SELECT u.id, u.openId, u.name, u.email, u.role, m.id as memberId FROM users u LEFT JOIN members m ON u.id = m.userId WHERE u.openId = (SELECT value FROM (SELECT 'OWNER_OPEN_ID' as value) as env_var) LIMIT 1;
